Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DETLEVEL_3D_OFF then end if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off
if bMigrationRotZ then if (GLOB_CONTEXT <> 2 & GLOB_CONTEXT <> 5) then addy -waveHeight/2 muly -1 mulx -1 rotz 90 endif endif
! --- Vertical Cut Length and Position Adjustment
length_proj = 0 pos_proj = 0
if ABS(rotation) > EPS then length_plus = ABS(waveHeight*TAN(rotation))
if rotation > 0 then if iTopCut = 1 then length_proj = length_proj + length_plus pos_proj = 0 endif else if iBottomCut = 1 then length_proj = length_proj + length_plus pos_proj = -length_plus endif endif endif
!============================================================================= ! Hotspot Editing !=============================================================================
unID = 1 + 3
!--- Angle Editing --- hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID,rotation, 6 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 1, 0, 0, unID,rotation, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, 0, 0, unID,rotation, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot length/2*cos(rotation), 0, eps+length/2*sin(rotation), unID,rotation, 5 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, B, 0, unID,rotation, 6 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 1, B, 0, unID,rotation, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, B, 0, unID,rotation, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot length/2*cos(rotation), B, eps+length/2*sin(rotation), unID,rotation, 5 : unID=unID+1
roty -rotation !--- Length Editing hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, length, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, 0, 0, unID, length, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot length, 0, 0, unID, length, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, B/2, 0, unID, length, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, B/2, 0, unID, length, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot length, B/2, 0, unID, length, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, B, 0, unID, length, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, B, 0, unID, length, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot length, B, 0, unID, length, 2 : unID=unID+1
unID=unID+3 !--- Width Editing hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, width, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, -0.001, 0, unID, width, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, width, 0, unID, width, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot length, 0, 0, unID, width, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot length, -0.001, 0, unID, width, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot length, width, 0, unID, width, 2 : unID=unID+1
!============================================================================= ! Feedback Mode !=============================================================================
if GLOB_CONTEXT > 22 & GLOB_CONTEXT < 29 then block length, width, waveHeight
end endif
del 1
!============================================================================= ! Model Mode !=============================================================================
addy B cutplane -90 !! cutting width B del 1
pen gs_cont_pen material mat1
if abs(waveLength) < EPS then end
v = A sumw = 0
if abs(rotation)>EPS and abs(abs(rotation)-90)>EPS then if iBottomCut = 1 then rotz 90 cutplane -90 del 1 endif if iTopCut = 1 then addx A2 rotz 90 cutplane 90 del 2 endif endif
roty -rotation addx length rotz 90 addy length rotx 90
if angCut4 > EPS then roty 90 add 0, 0, cut_width_4 roty angCut4+90 cutplane del 3 endif
if angCut3 > EPS then roty 90 add 0, 0, B-cut_width_3 roty 90-angCut3 cutplane del 3 endif
if angCut2 > EPS then roty 90 add -length, 0, cut_width_2 roty -90-angCut2 cutplane del 3 endif
if angCut1 > EPS then roty 90 add -length, 0, B-cut_width_1 roty angCut1-90 cutplane del 3 endif
!!! block width, waveHeight, length !--- check cutting---
!--- Profile 1 ---
if iProfiles = 1 then alpha=atn((width_bottom-width_upper)/2/waveHeight)
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE then for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, 0.75*poc1*not(bSimple3DProjection), bSimple3DProjection put sumw+poc1, 0, bSimple3DProjection put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2, 0, 0
if gs_resol > 24 then put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h1*tan(alpha), kiem_h1, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h1*tan(alpha)-kiem*cos(alpha), kiem_h1+kiem*sin(alpha), 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h2*tan(alpha)-kiem*cos(alpha), kiem_h2+kiem*sin(alpha), 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h2*tan(alpha), kiem_h2, 0 endif
put sumw+waveLength/2-width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-poc2, waveHeight, bSimple3DProjection put sumw+waveLength/2, waveHeight-0.75*poc2*not(bSimple3DProjection), bSimple3DProjection put sumw+waveLength/2+poc2, waveHeight, bSimple3DProjection put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0
if gs_resol > 24 then put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2+(waveHeight-kiem_h2)*tan(alpha), kiem_h2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2+(waveHeight-kiem_h2)*tan(alpha)+kiem*cos(alpha), kiem_h2+kiem*sin(alpha), 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2-kiem_h1*tan(alpha)+kiem*cos(alpha), kiem_h1+kiem*sin(alpha), 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2-kiem_h1*tan(alpha), kiem_h1, 0 endif
put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2, 0, 0 put sumw+waveLength-poc1, 0, bSimple3DProjection put sumw+waveLength, 0.75*poc1*not(bSimple3DProjection), bSimple3DProjection next sumw
addz pos_proj extrude NSP/3,0,0,length+length_proj,48, get(NSP) del 1 else thk_corr = (width_upper/2-width_bottom/2)*(thickness/waveHeight)
put sumw-poc1, 0, thickness/2, 0
for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, 0, 0.75*poc1-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+poc1, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2-thk_corr, 0, thickness/2, 0
if gs_resol > 24 then put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h1*tan(alpha), 0, kiem_h1-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h1*tan(alpha)-kiem*cos(alpha), 0, kiem_h1+kiem*sin(alpha)-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h2*tan(alpha)-kiem*cos(alpha), 0, kiem_h2+kiem*sin(alpha)-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h2*tan(alpha), 0, kiem_h2-thickness/2, 0 endif
put sumw+waveLength/2-width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-poc2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2, 0, waveHeight-0.75*poc2-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+poc2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0
if gs_resol > 24 then put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2+(waveHeight-kiem_h2)*tan(alpha), 0, kiem_h2-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2+(waveHeight-kiem_h2)*tan(alpha)+kiem*cos(alpha), 0, kiem_h2+kiem*sin(alpha)-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2-kiem_h1*tan(alpha)+kiem*cos(alpha), 0, kiem_h1+kiem*sin(alpha)-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2-kiem_h1*tan(alpha), 0, kiem_h1-thickness/2, 0 endif
put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2+thk_corr, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength-poc1, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength, 0, 0.75*poc1-thickness/2, 0 next sumw
put sumw+waveLength+1, 0, thickness/2, 0
addz pos_proj mulz -1 rotx -90 addz thickness/2 tube 4, NSP/4, 1+2+4+8+16+32+0+0, 0, 0, 0, length+length_proj, 0, 0, length+length_proj, -thickness, 0, 0, -thickness, 0,
get(NSP) del 4 endif endif
!--- Profile 2 ---
if iProfiles = 2 then if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE then for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, waveHeight, 1 put sumw+width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0 put sumw+width_bottom/2, 0, 0 put sumw+waveLength-width_bottom/2, 0, 0 put sumw+waveLength-width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0 put sumw+waveLength, waveHeight, 1 next sumw
addz pos_proj extrude NSP/3,0,0,length+length_proj,48, get(NSP) del 1 else thk_corr = (width_upper/2-width_bottom/2)*(thickness/waveHeight)
put -1, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0
for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+width_bottom/2+thk_corr, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength-width_bottom/2-thk_corr, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength-width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 next sumw
put sumw+waveLength+1, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0
addz pos_proj mulz -1 rotx -90 addz thickness/2 tube 4, NSP/4, 1+2+4+8+16+32+0+0, 0, 0, 0, length+length_proj, 0, 0, length+length_proj, -thickness, 0, 0, -thickness, 0,
get(NSP) del 4 endif endif
!--- Profile 3 ---
if iProfiles = 3 then if bProfiledMigrationStart then ! --- Correct Positioning during Forward Migration if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, 0, 0 put sumw+waveLength*3/8-width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0 put sumw+waveLength*3/8+width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0 put sumw+waveLength*3/8+width_bottom/2, 0, 0 put sumw+waveLength, 0, 0 next sumw
addz pos_proj extrude NSP/3,0,0,length+length_proj,48, get(NSP) del 1 else thk_corr = (width_upper/2-width_bottom/2)*(thickness/waveHeight)
put sumw-1, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw-eps/10, 0, thickness/2, 0
for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength*3/8-width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength*3/8+width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength*3/8+width_bottom/2+thk_corr,0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength, 0, thickness/2, 0 next sumw
put sumw+waveLength+1, 0, thickness/2, 0
addz pos_proj mulz -1 rotx -90 addz thickness/2 tube 4, NSP/4, 1+2+4+8+16+32+0+0, 0, 0, 0, length+length_proj, 0, 0, length+length_proj, -thickness, 0, 0, -thickness, 0,
get(NSP) del 4 endif else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, 0, 1 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2, 0, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2, 0, 0 put sumw+waveLength, 0, 1 next sumw
addz pos_proj extrude NSP/3,0,0,length+length_proj,48, get(NSP) del 1 else thk_corr = (width_upper/2-width_bottom/2)*(thickness/waveHeight)
put sumw-1, 0, thickness/2, 0
for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2-thk_corr, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2+thk_corr, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength, 0, thickness/2, 0 next sumw
put sumw+waveLength+1, 0, thickness/2, 0
addz pos_proj mulz -1 rotx -90 addz thickness/2 tube 4, NSP/4, 1+2+4+8+16+32+0+0, 0, 0, 0, length+length_proj, 0, 0, length+length_proj, -thickness, 0, 0, -thickness, 0,
get(NSP) del 4 endif endif endif
!--- Profile 4 ---
if iProfiles = 4 then alpha=atn((width_bottom-width_upper)/2/waveHeight)
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE then for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, 0, 1 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2, 0, 0
if gs_resol > 24 then put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h1*tan(alpha), kiem_h1, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h1*tan(alpha)-kiem*cos(alpha), kiem_h1+kiem*sin(alpha), 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h2*tan(alpha)-kiem*cos(alpha), kiem_h2+kiem*sin(alpha), 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h2*tan(alpha), kiem_h2, 0 endif
put sumw+waveLength/2-width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2, waveHeight, 0
if gs_resol > 24 then put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2+(waveHeight-kiem_h2)*tan(alpha), kiem_h2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2+(waveHeight-kiem_h2)*tan(alpha)+kiem*cos(alpha), kiem_h2+kiem*sin(alpha), 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2-kiem_h1*tan(alpha)+kiem*cos(alpha), kiem_h1+kiem*sin(alpha), 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2-kiem_h1*tan(alpha), kiem_h1, 0 endif
put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2, 0, 0 put sumw+waveLength, 0, 1 next sumw
addz pos_proj extrude NSP/3,0,0,length+length_proj,48, get(NSP) del 1 else thk_corr = (width_upper/2-width_bottom/2)*(thickness/waveHeight)
put sumw-1, 0, thickness/2, 0
for sumw=0 to B step waveLength put sumw, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2-thk_corr, 0, thickness/2, 0
if gs_resol >= 24 then put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h1*tan(alpha), 0, kiem_h1-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h1*tan(alpha)-kiem*cos(alpha), 0, kiem_h1+kiem*sin(alpha)-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h2*tan(alpha)-kiem*cos(alpha), 0, kiem_h2+kiem*sin(alpha)-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2-width_bottom/2+kiem_h2*tan(alpha), 0, kiem_h2-thickness/2, 0 endif
put sumw+waveLength/2-width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2, 0, waveHeight-thickness/2, 0
if gs_resol >= 24 then put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2+(waveHeight-kiem_h2)*tan(alpha), 0, kiem_h2-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_upper/2+(waveHeight-kiem_h2)*tan(alpha)+kiem*cos(alpha), 0, kiem_h2+kiem*sin(alpha)-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2-kiem_h1*tan(alpha)+kiem*cos(alpha), 0, kiem_h1+kiem*sin(alpha)-thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2-kiem_h1*tan(alpha), 0, kiem_h1-thickness/2, 0 endif
put sumw+waveLength/2+width_bottom/2+thk_corr, 0, thickness/2, 0 put sumw+waveLength, 0, thickness/2, 0 next sumw
put sumw+waveLength+1, 0, thickness/2, 0
addz pos_proj mulz -1 rotx -90 addz thickness/2 tube 4, NSP/4, 1+2+4+8+16+32+0+0, 0, 0, 0, length+length_proj, 0, 0, length+length_proj, -thickness, 0, 0, -thickness, 0,
get(NSP) del 4 endif endif
!--- Profile 5 ---
if iProfiles = 5 then resol gs_resol
nWaves = INT(width/waveLength) + 1
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE then wh = waveHeight dw = waveLength/4 wAngle = ATN(wh/2 / dw)*2 dh = dw / TAN(wAngle) rWave = dh + wh/2
sumw = 0 put 0, wh/2+0.001, 0 for i=1 to nWaves put sumw+0, -wh/2, 79 put sumw+0, dh, 900 put rWave, wAngle, 4079 put sumw+dw*2, -dh, 900 put rWave, -wAngle*2, 4079 put sumw+dw*4, dh, 900 put rWave, wAngle, 4079 put sumw+dw*4, -wh/2, 15
sumw = waveLength*i next i put sumw, wh/2+0.001, 0
addz pos_proj
cutdist = 1 roty 180 cutplane del 1 addz length+length_proj cutplane del 1
addz -cutdist addy waveHeight/2 prism_ NSP/3,length+length_proj+cutdist*2, get(NSP) del 2
cutend cutend
del 1 else wh = waveHeight - thickness dw = waveLength/4 wAngle = ATN(wh/2 / dw)*2 dh = dw / TAN(wAngle) rWave = dh + wh/2
sumw = 0 for i=1 to nWaves put sumw+0, -waveHeight/2, 79 put sumw+0, dh, 900 put rWave+thickness/2, wAngle, 4079 put sumw+dw*2, -dh, 900 put rWave-thickness/2, -wAngle*2, 4079 put sumw+dw*4, dh, 900 put rWave+thickness/2, wAngle, 4079 put sumw+dw*4, -waveHeight/2, 15
sumw = waveLength*i next i
sumw = nWaves*waveLength for i=1 to nWaves put sumw-0, -waveHeight/2+thickness, 79 put sumw-0, dh, 900 put rWave-thickness/2, -wAngle, 4079 put sumw-dw*2, -dh, 900 put rWave+thickness/2, wAngle*2, 4079 put sumw-dw*4, dh, 900 put rWave-thickness/2, -wAngle, 4079 put sumw-dw*4, -waveHeight/2+thickness, 15
sumw = sumw-waveLength next i
addz pos_proj addy waveHeight/2 prism_ NSP/3,length+length_proj, get(NSP) del 2 endif endif
if angCut1 > EPS then cutend if angCut2 > EPS then cutend if angCut3 > EPS then cutend if angCut4 > EPS then cutend
del 5
if abs(rotation)>eps and abs(abs(rotation)-90)>eps then if iTopCut = 1 then cutend endif if iBottomCut = 1 then cutend endif endif
cutend
if bMigrationRotZ then if (GLOB_CONTEXT <> 2 & GLOB_CONTEXT <> 5) then del 4 endif endif
end
Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen unID = 1
if bMigrationRotZ then add2 0,-waveHeight/2 mul2 -1,-1 rot2 90 endif
!============================================================================= ! Hotspot Editing !=============================================================================
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, width, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, -0.001, unID, width, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, width, unID, width, 2 : unID=unID+1
if abs(rotation-90) < eps or abs(rotation+90) < eps then hotspot2 -A2, 0, unID, width, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -A2, -0.001, unID, width, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -A2, width, unID, width, 2 : unID=unID+1 else hotspot2 A2, 0, unID, width, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A2, -0.001, unID, width, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A2, width, unID, width, 2 : unID=unID+1 endif
!============================================================================= ! 2D Symbol !=============================================================================
set fill gs_fill_type line_type gs_line_type
if abs(abs(rotation)-90)>eps then !--- Make Length stretchable hotspot2 0, 0, unID, A2, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -0.001, 0, unID, A2, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A2, 0, unID, A2, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0, width, unID, A2, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -0.001, width, unID, A2, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A2, width, unID, A2, 2 : unID=unID+1
line2 0,B/2,0.1,B/2
if gs_detlevel_2D_m = DETLEVEL_2D_CONTOUR or gs_detlevel_2D_m = DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE then ! --- Contour and Simple 2D if angCut1 < EPS then cut_width_1 = EPS if angCut2 < EPS then cut_width_2 = EPS if angCut3 < EPS then cut_width_3 = EPS if angCut4 < EPS then cut_width_4 = EPS
poly2_b 9, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, cut_width_4, 1, 0, B-cut_width_3, 1, cut_width_3*tan(angCut3) * cos(rotation), B, 1, A2-cut_width_1*tan(angCut1) * cos(rotation), B, 1, A2, B-cut_width_1, 1, A2, cut_width_2, 1, A2-cut_width_2*tan(angCut2) * cos(rotation), 0, 1, cut_width_4*tan(angCut4) * cos(rotation), 0, 1, 0, cut_width_4, -1
if gs_detlevel_2D_m = DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE then if GLOB_SCALE < 201 then waveStep = waveLength*4 if GLOB_SCALE < 101 then waveStep = waveLength*2 if GLOB_SCALE < 51 then waveStep = waveLength
line_type wave_line_type sumw = 0 for sumw=0 to B step waveStep if sumw>0 and sumw<B then line2 0, sumw, A2, sumw endif next sumw endif endif else ! --- Detailed 2D
if bMigrationRotZ and GLOB_CONTEXT = 22 then rot2 90 add2 0,waveHeight/2 endif
pen gs_fill_pen line_type gs_line_type set fill gs_fill_type project2{3} 3, 270, 3+32, 15, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 90 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE, gs_resol = 12, bSimple3DProjection = 1
pen gs_cont_pen project2{3} 3, 270, 2+32, 15, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 90 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE, gs_resol = 12, bSimple3DProjection = 1
if bMigrationRotZ and GLOB_CONTEXT = 22 then del 2 endif
if iProfiles = 5 then waveStep = waveLength
line_type wave_line_type sumw = 0 for sumw=0 to B step waveStep if sumw>0 and sumw<B then line2 0, sumw, A2, sumw endif next sumw endif endif
else ! --- Vertical Sheet line_type gs_line_type set fill gs_fill_type
if bMigrationRotZ and GLOB_CONTEXT = 22 then rot2 -270 add2 0,waveHeight/2 endif
if gs_detlevel_2D_m = DETLEVEL_2D_CONTOUR or gs_detlevel_2D_m = DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE then ! --- Contour and Simple 2D project2{3} 3, 270, 32+3, 1+2+4+8, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 90 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE, gs_resol = 12, bSimple3DProjection = 1 else project2{3} 3, 270, 32+3, 1+2+4+8, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 90 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = DETLEVEL_3D_DETAILED, gs_resol = 36 endif
if bMigrationRotZ and GLOB_CONTEXT = 22 then del 2 endif
endif
if bMigrationRotZ then del 3
end
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS = 0.0001
!============================================================================= ! String Resources !=============================================================================
dim stProfileTypes[5] stProfileTypes[1] = `Профилированный Лист 1` stProfileTypes[2] = `Профилированный Лист 2` stProfileTypes[3] = `Профилированный Лист 3` stProfileTypes[4] = `Профилированный Лист 4` stProfileTypes[5] = `Профилированный Лист 5`
dim stCuttingTypes[2] stCuttingTypes[1] = `Вертикальный` stCuttingTypes[2] = `Перпендикулярно Листу`
dim stDetlevel2DValues[3] stDetlevel2DValues[1] = `Контур` stDetlevel2DValues[2] = `Простой` stDetlevel2DValues[3] = `Детальный`
dim stDetlevel3DValues[3] stDetlevel3DValues[1] = `Простой` stDetlevel3DValues[2] = `Детальный` stDetlevel3DValues[3] = `Откл.`
DETLEVEL_2D_CONTOUR = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 2 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 3
DETLEVEL_3D_OFF = 0 DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_3D_DETAILED = 2
CUT_VERTICAL = 1 CUT_PERPENDICULAR = 2
!============================================================================= ! Calculations !=============================================================================
nTabs = 3
!--- Check Working Unit ---
actformat = REQUEST ("Working_length_unit", "", format_string) n = SPLIT (format_string, "%s %n %s" ,flag, prec, convspec)

hideparameter all "A", "B", "Zzyzx"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "gs_resol" range[3,)
!============================================================================= ! Profile types and sizes !=============================================================================
values{2} "iProfiles" 1, stProfileTypes[1], 2, stProfileTypes[2], 3, stProfileTypes[3], 4, stProfileTypes[4], 5, stProfileTypes[5]
values "size" profileDefaults, `Специальный`
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iProfiles" then if iProfiles = 1 then size = profileDefaults[1] if iProfiles = 2 then size = profileDefaults[1] if iProfiles = 3 then size = profileDefaults[3] if iProfiles = 4 then size = profileDefaults[1] if iProfiles = 5 then size = profileDefaults[3] parameters size = size endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "size" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iProfiles" then for i = 1 to vardim1(enabledDefaults) if enabledDefaults[i] > 0 then if size = profileDefaults[enabledDefaults[i]] then waveHeight = profileSizes[i][1] waveLength = profileSizes[i][2] parameters waveHeight = waveHeight, waveLength = waveLength
i = vardim1(enabledDefaults) ! break endif endif next i else actSize = str(sizeFormat, waveHeight) + strSeparatorCharacter + str(sizeFormat, waveLength) bCustom = 1 for i = 1 to vardim1(profileDefaults) if actSize = profileDefaults[i] then bCustom = 0 next i
if bCustom then size = `Специальный` else size = actSize endif parameters size = size endif
values "thickness" range (0, )
!============================================================================= ! Profile wave upper and bottom defaults, ranges !=============================================================================
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iProfiles" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "size" then if iProfiles = 1 then width_upper = 0.1225 width_bottom = 0.1875 endif
if iProfiles = 2 then width_upper = 0.0625 width_bottom = 0.0285 endif
if iProfiles = 3 then if size = profileDefaults[1] then width_upper = waveLength-0.0270833 width_bottom = waveLength-0.018396 else if size = profileDefaults[2] then width_upper = waveLength-0.0425 width_bottom = waveLength-0.02545 else if size = profileDefaults[3] then width_upper = waveLength-0.04333 width_bottom = waveLength-0.02943 else if size = profileDefaults[4] then width_upper = waveLength-0.0635 width_bottom = waveLength-0.04445 else if size = profileDefaults[5] then width_upper = waveLength-0.06985 width_bottom = waveLength-0.0381 else width_upper = waveLength-0.04333 width_bottom = waveLength-0.02943 endif endif endif endif endif endif
if iProfiles = 4 then if size = profileDefaults[1] then width_upper = waveLength-0.063 width_bottom = waveLength-0.0428 else width_upper = waveLength-0.04333 width_bottom = waveLength-0.02943 endif endif
parameters width_upper = width_upper, width_bottom = width_bottom endif
!--- Profile 1 ---
if iProfiles = 1 then values "width_bottom" range [0.026, waveLength - 0.026] values "width_upper" range [0.026, waveLength - 0.026]
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "width_upper" then if width_bottom < width_upper then width_bottom = width_upper endif if waveLength - 0.026 < width_upper then waveLength = width_upper + 0.026 endif else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "width_bottom" then if width_upper > width_bottom then width_upper = width_bottom endif if waveLength - 0.026 < width_bottom then waveLength = width_bottom + 0.026 endif else if width_bottom > waveLength - 0.026 then width_bottom = waveLength - 0.026 endif if width_upper > width_bottom then width_upper = width_bottom endif endif endif
parameters width_bottom = width_bottom, width_upper = width_upper, waveLength = waveLength endif
!--- Profile 2 ---
if iProfiles = 2 then values "width_bottom" range (0, width_upper] values "width_upper" range [width_bottom, waveLength) endif
!--- Profile 3, Profile 4 ---
if iProfiles = 3 or iProfiles = 4 then values "width_bottom" range [width_upper, waveLength) values "width_upper" range (0, width_bottom] endif
!--- Profile 5 ---
if iProfiles = 5 then lock "width_upper", "width_bottom" hideparameter "width_upper", "width_bottom"
if waveLength < waveHeight * 2 then waveLength = waveHeight * 2 parameters waveLength = waveLength endif endif
!============================================================================= ! Detail Levels !=============================================================================
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE, stDetlevel3DValues[1], DETLEVEL_3D_DETAILED, stDetlevel3DValues[2], DETLEVEL_3D_OFF, stDetlevel3DValues[3]
values{2} "gs_detlevel_2D_m" DETLEVEL_2D_CONTOUR, stDetlevel2DValues[1], DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE, stDetlevel2DValues[2], DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED, stDetlevel2DValues[3]
!============================================================================= ! Sheet cutting !=============================================================================
values{2} "iTopCut" 1, stCuttingTypes[1], 2, stCuttingTypes[2]
values{2} "iBottomCut" 1, stCuttingTypes[1], 2, stCuttingTypes[2]
!============================================================================= ! Cut parameters !=============================================================================
values "rotation" range [-90,90]
if abs(rotation)<eps or abs(rotation-90) < eps then lock "iTopCut", "iBottomCut" endif
if abs(angCut1)<eps then lock "cut_width_1" if abs(angCut2)<eps then lock "cut_width_2" if abs(angCut3)<eps then lock "cut_width_3" if abs(angCut4)<eps then lock "cut_width_4"
values "angCut1" range [0, 90) values "angCut2" range [0, 90) values "angCut3" range [0, 90) values "angCut4" range [0, 90)
values "cut_width_1" range [0, width] values "cut_width_2" range [0, width-cut_width_1*(angCut1>0)] values "cut_width_3" range [0, width] values "cut_width_4" range [0, width-cut_width_3*(angCut3>0)]
if iProfiles = 1 then values "waveLength" range [0.052, ) values "waveHeight" range (0, ) else if iProfiles = 5 then values "waveLength" range [waveHeight * 2, ) values "waveHeight" range (0, ) else values "waveLength" range (0, ) values "waveHeight" range (0, ) endif endif
values "width" range (0, ) values "length" range (0, ) values "A2" range (0, )
! --- Sizes ---------------------------------------------------------------------
if abs(rotation-90) < eps or abs(rotation+90) < eps then A = waveHeight parameters A = A else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" then length = abs(A/cos(rotation) + waveHeight*abs(tan(rotation))) parameters length = length else A = abs((length-waveHeight*abs(tan(rotation))) * cos(rotation)) parameters A = A endif endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" then width = B parameters width = width else B = width parameters B = B endif
if abs(rotation) < eps then parameters ZZYZX = waveHeight lock "ZZYZX" else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ZZYZX" then length = abs((ZZYZX - waveHeight*cos(rotation)) / sin(rotation)) parameters length = length else ZZYZX = abs(length*sin(rotation) + waveHeight*cos(rotation)) parameters ZZYZX = ZZYZX endif endif
if abs(rotation-90) < eps or abs(rotation+90) < eps then A2 = waveHeight parameters A2 = A2 else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A2" then length = A2/cos(rotation) parameters length = length else A2 = length * cos(rotation) parameters A2 = A2 endif endif
